,503,505,506,508,509,511,512,514,515,518],{},"To switch styles, you delete all of these, then run ",[37,504,177],{}," again (remember ",[37,507,124],{}," and ",[37,510,53],{}," have to go too). One heads-up: don't delete ",[37,513,468],{}," — that's a config file ",[37,516,517],{},"@babel"," needs.",[17,520,521],{},[44,522],{"alt":133,"src":523},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F7cxRsxu.png",[17,525,526,527,529,530,453,532,534],{},"Again, ignore ",[37,528,53],{}," — the important part is the ",[37,531,69],{},[37,533,65],{},". You'll see the packages got replaced with these:",[72,536,537,541,545,549,554,558,562,566],{},[75,538,539],{},[37,540,463],{},[75,542,543],{},[37,544,468],{},[75,546,547],{},[37,548,473],{},[75,550,551],{},[37,552,553],{},"@vue\u002Feslint-config-airbnb",[75,555,556],{},[37,557,79],{},[75,559,560],{},[37,561,89],{},[75,563,564],{},[37,565,499],{},[75,567,568],{},[37,569,570],{},"eslint-plugin-vuejs-accessibility",[17,572,573,574,576,577,508,580,54],{},"Lay the two side by side and you'll see the installed packages are completely different — not to mention that ",[37,575,177],{}," also tweaks some other files along the way, like ",[37,578,579],{},".editorconfig",[37,581,582],{},"babel.config.js",[17,584,585,586,590],{},"So honestly, instead of swapping styles by hand, it's often faster and safer to just ",[587,588,589],"strong",{},"create a new project"," and migrate your code over.",[17,592,593,594,600],{},"The example code is all ",[28,595,599],{"href":596,"rel":597},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Feslint-toggle-example",[598],"nofollow","over here"," if you want to download it and play around.",[602,603,604],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html .d